The vision is to create a global stock and secured market, without any boundaries or time limits, also the database will put some leading companies and investors in contact through the database.
However, the basic purpose of business is of a stock exchange which provides a market place for companies and investors that wishes to raise money, the business plan also exhibits to offer companies wishing to raise money on buying and selling shares which are sold to investors, Moreover, it mainly facilitates the exchange of shares, buying of shares and involvement of communication between shareholder and share buyers.
